h1. Ground Sphere Safety Procedures v0.2

{{toc}}

h2. Introduction

Since this device is receive only, there are no operational safety procedures outlined at this time. This document may be modified at any time, and a notice should be posted to the forums when that happens. Check back to this document frequently to ensure that you have the latest safety information.

h2. Additional Safety Information

The "American Radio Relay League":http://www.arrl.org/ safety committee has "safety information and explanations":http://www.arrl.org/arrl-rf-safety-committee that can be reviewed before operating Ground Sphere. 